law.catch_line: Federal statutes and regulations not to be incorporated by reference.
law.text: Federal statutes and regulations shall not be incorporated by reference. If applicable, they shall be cited in the "RELATES TO" and "STATUTORY AUTHORITY" references in a proposed administrative regulation.
law.history: Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 11, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 516, sec. 9, effective July 13, 1990.
